(137, 'Od ateizmu k prekladu Biblie', '100317', '', '<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"margin: auto; border: medium none; height: 279px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"900\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes;\">\r\n<td style=\" border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"800\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \">Nap├¡sala: Mary┬áTindall, Nemecko<br /></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \">Preklad: Wycliffe Slovakia<br /></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \">Fotografie: Dale┬áPeacock </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\"><em>Kv├┤li zachovaniu bezpe─ìnosti spom├¡nan├¢ch post├ív v ─ìl├ínku pou┼¥├¡vame pseudonymy a nezobrazujeme ich tv├íre.</em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img src=\"images/stories/viac/Pribehy/Reza/549820160411.jpg\" border=\"0\" width=\"600\" height=\"400,8\" /><br /></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \">Vyrastaj├║c v┬áneslobodnej z├ípado├ízijskej krajine, Reza nikdy neprijal islam, ktor├¢ je v├ñ─ì┼íinov├¢m n├íbo┼¥enstvom tejto krajiny. Naopak, pova┼¥oval sa za ateistu. Na p├┤de svojej vysokej ┼íkoly otvorene vyjadroval svoje n├ízory. Jedn├®ho d┼êa up├║tali jeho sekul├írne postoje pozornos┼Ñ pol├¡cie. Zabavili mu knihy a┬átajne ho odvliekli do v├ñzenia. Jeho rodi─ìia ho tri mesiace h─¥adali. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \">Nakoniec sa R